social_posts.post_text: Tell em send 2…1 won’t get the job done 🥷🏾
SUPER BOWL!!! we not done yet! #ringchasin #stillhere
7on7 summer classic was lit! Shout out to all the teams that participated. Special thanks to Malik and the KVS team for making it happen!!🥇
I’m not wavered by my situation. I worship a God who gives me life and strength daily. I’ll bounce back in due time! Thank you for all the thoughts and prayers❤️‍🔥

Join us tomorrow for an exciting event with Philadelphia eagles  players myself and Milton Williams! Kids can enjoy complimentary haircuts, hot chocolate, meet the players, and even receive a signed item. Give back this holiday season with this special gathering!

Come celebrate the holidays with us next week, December 20th, at @phillysocialhouse - kicking off at 3 PM. No need to RSVP—just bring your holiday cheer!

We want to give back to all of you through my nonprofit, Catalyst 4 Change. We’ll have light bites, signed merch, Eagles vs Giants ticket raffle , and young ones get a special gift of choice to take home!

Your presence will make the celebration complete—join us and let’s make this holiday unforgettable! 🎄
